title: Week 13 NFL Recap, Analysis; Ravens run continues, Pats falter (Football 12/2)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 12 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 12 games on the Sunday slate including Patriots-Texans (4:00), 49ers-Ravens (20:10), Browns-Steelers (30:45), Chiefs-Raiders (40:45), Titans-Colts (48:00), Eagles-Dolphins (57:00), Bengals-Jets (1:09:15), Redskins-Panthers (1:17:00), Jags-Bucs (1:20:45), Rams-Cardinals (1:27:15), Giants-Packers (1:31:00) and Chargers-Broncos (1:40:00).
